{"tid":2265425,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"留美華生控訴 家人受脅迫做卧底","createTime":"2020-10-31T12:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T14:59:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e46a0e6cfa3a423e0a4181b113ace6c9d5b8cf59","tid":2265425,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T12:19:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201031/CIA642RKC5C23OX3KVST4IKHFA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201031%2FCIA642RKC5C23OX3KVST4IKHFA%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak0lZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=ecd32ba6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201031%2FCIA642RKC5C23OX3KVST4IKHFA%2F&h=9ccd1e22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201031/CIA642RKC5C23OX3KVST4IKHFA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n留美華生控訴 家人受脅迫做卧底<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VITNbO4Pyi_UKOKJeq-rwtIOsbY=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HAZW2RE2URBL3PXZIJMQOWCOYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVITNbO4Pyi_UKOKJeq-rwtIOsbY%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHAZW2RE2URBL3PXZIJMQOWCOYY.jpg&h=f8d79ef2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■留美中國留學生據報遭國保要求「戴罪立功」。<br />\n<br />\n外媒近日引述在美的中國留學生控訴，中國國保透過威脅其家人，禁止他發表批評中共言論，還要他做中共卧底，在網上暗中收集批評北京的言論，要他「戴罪立功」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n須收集網上反京言論<br />\n<br />\n中國留學生李陶陶（化名）透露，今年在網絡實名發表批評北京言論，未料兩周後，國保人員不斷找他在國內父母麻煩，要他們到警局報到及沒收護照。李稱，國保常在美國時間凌晨致電給他指示，包括要他交出社交平台密碼，不准發表不利中國言論，還要他在社交平台做卧底，要他截圖通報批評中國發言，指這是「戴罪立功」，以後回去不抓他，但從來不說明其罪，只說他「反華」、「侮辱國家」。<br />\n<br />\n2005年叛逃的前中國駐澳洲外交官員陳用林表示，國保不斷介。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n此外，美國司法部近日起訴、逮捕以中國非法代理人身份在美國參。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美國之音/澎湃網"},{"pid":"b2490dc296ad232549b063db9d5d0656f263e6e7","tid":2265425,"uid":55913,"like":4,